  "body": "# Components\r\n\r\n## Application Security Management (WAF)\r\n\r\n* :bug: Add http.response.headers.content-type span tag on blocking responses (#10884 - @jandro996)\r\n* :bug: Fix ObjectIntrospection exposing JDK internal toString() to the WAF (#10882 - @jandro996)\r\n\r\n## Profiling\r\n\r\n* :sparkles: Update Java profiler library to [1.39.0](https://github.com/DataDog/java-profiler/releases/tag/v_1.38.0) (#10869 - @jbachorik) (contains also [1.38.0](https://github.com/DataDog/java-profiler/releases/tag/v_1.38.0))\r\n",
